"uid":238801,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T20:26:49.000Z","msg":"好耐冇試過痴咗線咁玩 乜都唔在乎咁玩 因為我覺得痴痴地 <br />\n聽日可以好幸福 唔用出街"},{"pid":"4fe88208ea1a6c7155f4a0153d483afcc3e79b3b","tid":1128424,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3309de74b9e5efe67df855acb2124209a44cae2b","tid":1128424,"uid":232378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T20:25:48.000Z","msg":"唔抵得人有？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T20:27:16.000Z","msg":"唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f03417d06e9395267f9373e5a8e3924af46657f","tid":1128424,"uid":238801,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T20:29:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嗰種 乜都唔再關我事 嘅感好好<br />\n我鐘意西住面咁做人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />鐘意想人唔好麻煩到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔再係諗人地點諗 做比人諗點諗嗰個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好舒服啊"},{"pid":"266f7c39e95e14c76c015bfb7ca84b74b377c707","tid":1128424,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T20:33:00.000Z","msg":"物以罕為貴 同你講 deleted <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點都好 只要keep住得唔到呢個state 就會deleted^^<br />\n火雞未食同第一啖之間係最高峰<br />\n諗下都覺得sad"},{"pid":"47828724595ccb05c6c7b55c96cc4eb2279a03b3","tid":1128424,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T20:34:03.000Z","msg":"我真係眼瞓到就嚟死<br />\n我抽到差點哮喘先去面對一屋一擔壓力已經很勇悍"},{"pid":"365198f099c78ac1b7df763e6b43ed773e5da3dc","tid":1128424,"uid":238801,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T20:37:01.000Z","msg":"我咩都唔想理住 唔想理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />覺得一瞓醒又要面對就<br />\n好唔想面對<br />\n<br />\n我覺得好似loop但我心入面對人呢樣嘢有恐懼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n覺得每個人都可以係假 每個人都有機會係冷血賤人或黑心<br />\n每個人都有機會做得出好多嘢<br />\n信乜唔好信曬 愈了解就愈想反感<br />\n但理智啲諗個個都係咁 你係唔suppose會要逃避<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啊啊啊"},{"pid":"2d0a2c18695f4916005efa1b85516895fc175d21","tid":1128424,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T20:38:29.000Z","msg":"應該係話對人呢樣嘢冇乜保證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見識過下限就唔會再信世界上有好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n指新認識嗰啲"},{"pid":"25f766ff4bb90a923930299feb8ec45ade8ca014","tid":1128424,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T20:39:14.000Z","msg":"發覺自己視力一日一日變差...."},{"pid":"c91aed93ad5f0b991162b5e255854e75836e916a","tid":1128424,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T20:41:24.000Z","msg":"覺得唔係真係咁有趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為好多嘢都好公式化<br />\n基本上你達某啲標準你就會做到<br />\n唔明有咩意思<br />\n我其實係我唔明咩叫有意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4baf48cb20e4dbf8c9defa068a65eeea9d936290","tid":1128424,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T20:45:01.000Z","msg":"顧人感受<br />\n顧你感受？<br />\n咁點解要顧人感受"},{"pid":"78f58179944e49de4bb95df74afc3b0973dc82ca","tid":1128424,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T20:46:39.000Z","msg":"有啲嘢你知你明你做唔代表人地同你一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n覺得曬氣但唔做又過唔到自己嗰關 原則<br />\n但惡頂咁點<br />\n<br />\n規矩係死人係生 但如果搓圓撳扁咁我係咪我"},{"pid":"773138c669f0e8977c24396e293b98c11b75e638","tid":1128424,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T20:48:20.000Z","msg":"原來會驚人係真 好厭倦認清一個人嘅為人嘅情況<br />\n唔係倦係直情驚 唔想了解佢係咩人 唔想知入面啲嘢幾撚骯髒"},{"pid":"02eeacec654a909237997758a32878c6a39da0a8","tid":1128424,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T20:50:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你愈了解一個人你只會愈嚟愈發現佢嘅唔好<br />\n冇咗光環效應之後只會直線下降<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n潔癖令我抗拒但現實冇得逃避"},{"pid":"733709697174bab4a31854d14f983261116dae08","tid":1128424,"uid":124256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T00:51:24.000Z","msg":"樓主冇人要"},{"pid":"e9efa060fccecbdda70e84feb3430744a48933ce","tid":1128424,"uid":55249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T01:11:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/482ee0/f/800x0/https://i.imgur.com/JoX8Gh4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discuss.com.hk%2Ft%2F482ee0%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FJoX8Gh4.jpg&h=9e5a5738&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0267ded586b131ec6e613003a0a14091102f00e4","tid":1128424,"uid":198990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T04:51:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/80cLZTo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F80cLZTo.png&h=bc088a57&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"121ea48956c6c6b743aa1de6021dcc301f59dfa9","tid":1128424,"uid":209432,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T05:00:59.000Z","msg":"咩叫「想笑而不語」<br />\n我睇到你打啲字就真係笑而不語喇"},{"pid":"41ae495707ddf91c32ca68eb0d49798358e08b6c","tid":1128424,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"733709697174bab4a31854d14f983261116dae08","tid":1128424,"uid":124256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T00:51:24.000Z","msg":"樓主冇人要"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T06:18:58.000Z","msg":"系<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}